      "line": null,
      "message": "It should be removed.  All the content in this submission is basically a draft of the final version of a spring-boot sparky.  The goal of the initial submission is to get enough of the solution in place to enable execution of the Nexus QI scan.\n\nThere is more cleanup that we need to do for sure.  For example, within the application module there are a bunch of files that are still ajsc-y that should be removed.  I'll make a change and remove them.\n\nI was keeping this particular file around until I figured out how to covert the PortalRestAPIProxy into a spring-boot construct.  Most likely it will be a Camel-Rest like the other ones, I just haven't finished that conversion yet.",
